                        <h2>PTE Exam Eligibility Criteria</h2>
                        <p>Pearson PLC Group, the administrative institution of the Pearson PTE Academic Exam, does not specify a PTE exam eligibility criteria for candidates looking to appear for the PTE Academic Exam.</p>
                        <div class="highlight-box">
                            <p>However, as a general rule, aspirants appearing for the PTE Academic exam should be at least <strong>16 years of age</strong> at the time of appearing for the PTE Academic test. Aspirants who are below 18 years of age need to get a parental consent form signed to take the PTE Academic test, as part of the PTE exam eligibility 2024.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

