                        <h2>Preparing For PTE Academic</h2>
                        <p>The PTE exam requires a minimum age of 16 years. The PTE exam is applicable to anybody over the age of 16, regardless of nationality or background. Pearson PLC group, the organization that administers the exam, has set no age limit or eligibility criteria, though it is preferable that the candidate be at least 16 years of age.</p>
                        <div class="highlight-box">
                            <p>There are two methods for preparing for PTE: self-study and coaching classes. Which path you take is determined on your level of language proficiency and comfort. You do not need to attend coaching classes if you are already fluent in English; you can prepare for the exam on your own. You only need to determine when you should begin preparing for PTE.</p>
